      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is suitable for someone looking for a functional daily driver that needs some TLC. The engine starts and runs reliably, though it shows its age with some minor fluid leaks and a noticeable vibration at highway speeds. The exterior has several scratches, small dents, and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a cracked dashboard. All major electronics work, though the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. It is a solid, honest car for the price, provided you are comfortable with its cosmetic flaws and upcoming maintenance needs.",
