    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. The double-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and communicative steering feedback inherent to the M-chassis. While the exterior",
