    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2018 Executive Sport Sedan in Obsidian Black Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and shows the pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor peppering on the hood from standard road use. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the charcoal Nappa leather interior remains firm and comfortable; the cabin is smoke-free and the dual-zone climate control blows ice-cold. All electronic components, including the navigation system and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean with no signs of fluid leaks. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed just 500 miles ago. The transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next chapter.",
